Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都沒關係的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所有往事盡懷抱
